title Become an active contributor to the PLDB

aftertext
 Do you seek programming language enlightenment? Why not seek that joyfully with colleagues while serving others, making an impact, and accumulating citations? Become an active contributor to the PLDB!

subsection Things you could do

list
 - Write an article
 - Adding or editing languages in the database
 - Adding or editing design patterns and examples in the database
 - Work on a data importer for a source like Wikipedia or Github
 - Discussing and improving the data schema
 - Working on improvements to the website or codebase

aftertext
 To get involved, start submitting pull requests, opening issues, or send an <a href="mailto:feedback@pldb.pub">email</a>.

